        div.card
            h3 Dance your heart out
            img#img2(src='../static/dance2.jpg', alt='dance')
            p We believe in dancing our heart out like no one is watching. 
        div.card
            h3 Professional Dancer
            img#img3(src='../static/dance4.jpg', alt='dance')
